<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Admin - eSante Mali</title>
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="{{ asset('images/esante.png') }}">
    <!-- Font Awesome (icônes) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            height: 100vh;
            background: url('{{ asset("images/fond.png") }}') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .overlay {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .logos {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .logos img {
            height: 85px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .logos img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 34px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #00e6b8;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 17px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .btn-login {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 25px;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c9a7, #00a8ff);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .btn-login i {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        .btn-login:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .welcome-message {
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            background: rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.9);
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 14px;
            animation: fadeOut 5s forwards;
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        }

        @keyframes fadeOut {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            80% { opacity: 1; }
            100% { opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; }
        }

        .glow {
            position: absolute;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 200, 0.15);
            filter: blur(100px);
            border-radius: 50%;
            top: 10%;
            left: 10%;
        }

        .title-icon {
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #00e6b8;
        }

        .text-icon {
            margin-right: 8px;
            color: #00e6b8;
        }

        .logos i {
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 30px;
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="glow"></div>

<!-- message bienvenue -->
<div class="welcome-message">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i>
    Bienvenue Administrateur eSante Mali — Veuillez vous connecter
</div>

<div class="overlay">

    <div class="card">

        <!-- logos -->
        <div class="logos">
            <img src="{{ asset('images/esante.png') }}" alt="eSante Mali">
                    <!-- titre -->
        <h1>
            eSante Mali
        </h1>
            <img src="{{ asset('images/mali.jpeg') }}" alt="Ministère de la Santé Mali">
        </div>
        <!-- description -->
        <p>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-notes-medical text-icon"></i>
            eSante Mali est une plateforme numérique moderne dédiée à la gestion intelligente du système de santé.
            Elle permet de gérer les patients, médecins, rendez-vous, dossiers médicaux et statistiques en temps réel.
        </p>

        <p style="margin-top:10px;">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-heart text-icon"></i>
            Notre objectif est de moderniser et digitaliser le système de santé du Mali pour plus d’efficacité et de transparence.
        </p>

        <!-- bouton -->
        <a href="{{ path('admin_login') }}" class="btn-login">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-right-to-bracket"></i>
            Se connecter
        </a>

    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>